        "text": "I will provide you combined summaries of various emails split into multiple tables. \nEach table has 4 columns: Sender, Subject, Summary, List of actions.\n\nCombine them into ONE single markdown table sorted by priority from high to low based on urgency of actions.\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n- Output ONLY the markdown table\n- NO headings, NO explanations, NO \"Merged table\" text\n- Start your response directly with | Sender |\n- End your response with the last table row\n\nData: {{ $json.combined_summaries }}",
